{"tha-ap267:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap267:0.2":"Padumukkhipavagga ","tha-ap267:0.3":"Bilalidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap267:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap267:1.2":"romaso nama pabbato; ","tha-ap267:1.3":"Tamhi pabbatapadamhi, ","tha-ap267:1.4":"samano bhavitindriyo. ","tha-ap267:2.1":"Bilaliyo gahetvana, ","tha-ap267:2.2":"samanassa adasaham; ","tha-ap267:2.3":"Anumodi mahaviro, ","tha-ap267:2.4":"sayambhu aparajito. ","tha-ap267:3.1":"Bilali te mama dinna, ","tha-ap267:3.2":"vippasannena cetasa; ","tha-ap267:3.3":"Bhave nibbattamanamhi, ","tha-ap267:3.4":"phalam nibbattatam tava. ","tha-ap267:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap267:4.2":"yam bilalimadasaham; ","tha-ap267:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap267:4.4":"bilaliya idam phalam. ","tha-ap267:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap267:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap267:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap267:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bilalidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap267:7.1":"Bilalidayakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}